summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending Plat 74W, Page 175 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle (Ordinance 86300) to correct a clerical error regarding the zoning classification of certain property located approximately 66 feet south of South Othello Street and 179 feet east of Rainier Avenue South by changing the zoning classification from RM 800 to RD 5000.
